Blockers: cron:e7885813 вЂ” zombie since ~16:40 UTC, needs disable\n\nвЂ” Orbis рџЊђ"}],"timestamp":1776186389832,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"df860b3c","seq":1150}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Skip."},{"type":"text","text":"\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":285,"output":11,"totalTokens":97043,"cacheRead":7778,"cacheWrite":88969,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776186390018,"responseId":"062da71776d57ccc4ddda851c5e62cf2","__openclaw":{"id":"139d0cac","seq":1151}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776186240053,"sessionId":"9102c1da-c3b5-4081-91fd-c19e9b3bb552","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":45487,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776152701090,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/9102c1da-c3b5-4081-91fd-c19e9b3bb552.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The session_send timed out. The Telegram session may be having issues again. Let me try again or report this as a delivery issue.\n\nActually, the instructions say to \"return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically.\" But I also have a task to send to group -5163901258. The timeout suggests the Telegram session isn't responding well.\n\nLet me just provide the report as a plain text reply since the delivery failed, as the instructions suggest.