otalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1776131194520,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted.","__openclaw":{"id":"9285c51d","seq":19}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776117647627,"sessionId":"ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":17388,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context to compose the daily briefing. Let me craft a clean status report for the Telegram group -5212380728.\n\nKey info:\n- Yesterday (2026-04-12): AHV Works review complete, session crash and recovery, BE behind 11 commits, FE synced\n- Today (2026-04-13): Fix AHV Works P0 issues (13 items), Stitch MCP wrapper test, stitch-connect skill update, BE merge decision pending\n- Blockers: BE is 11 commits behind remote on notification system, Lead decision needed for merge\n\nCurrent time is 10:00 PM UTC (10:00 PM Monday April 13), so this briefing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\n\n\nNow I'll format this as a status report."},{"type":"text","text":"рџЊ… **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\nрџ“… Monday, April 13, 2026\nвЏ° 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\n\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n\n**1пёЏвѓЈ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\n\nвњ… **AHV Works Review** вЂ” FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\nвњ… **Session Recovery** вЂ” Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\nвњ… **FE Sync** вЂ” Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop вњ…\nвњ… **DTLX/QLHV Systems** вЂ” Stable, shared DB architecture operational\nвњ… **34-Agent Ecosystem** вЂ” SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified вњ…\n\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n\n**2пёЏвѓЈ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\n\nрџ”ґ **P0 вЂ” AHV Works Fixes** вЂ” 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\nрџџЎ **Stitch MCP Wrapper** вЂ” Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\nрџџЎ **stitch-connect Skill** вЂ” Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\nрџ”µ **BE Notification System** вЂ” Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\n\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n\n**3пёЏвѓЈ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\nвљ пёЏ **BE Merge Conflict** вЂ” Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\n\nвљ пёЏ **Context Overflow Risk** вЂ” Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\n\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n\n**Pipeline Status:** рџџў HEALTHY\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\n\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nOrbis рџЊђ вЂ” Global Orchestrator"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":328,"output":570,"totalTokens":17958,"cacheRead":14121,"cacheWrite":2939,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776117671474,"responseId":"062c9aa87844c59bbd285766e62b966f","__openclaw":{"id":"faf39631","seq":7}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","label":"QLHV monitor run","displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-subagent-8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","delive